name: Aquascape: The Short Escape #003
description:
#003 / 004

back with a series of activities carried out during the pandemic to stay sane in a world that is quite crazy.

One activity that can calm the heart and mind is aquascape. a small aquarium with a very refreshing and relaxing visual appearance. sink into another world that feels even better. even though in reality it's not fine. at the very least, with an aquascape it can be both a remedy and a short escape.
